casebody.data:
Michael Daniel CUERO, Petitioner-Appellant,
v.
Scott KERNAN * , Respondent-Appellee. No. 12-55911 United States Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Filed September 19, 2018

ORDER

Scott Kernan has been substituted for his predecessor, Matthew Cate, as Secretary, California Department of Corrections and Rehabilitation.

In light of Kernan v. Cuero , ---- U.S. ----, 138 S.Ct. 4 , 199 L.Ed.2d 236 (2017), we affirm the judgment of the district court.

AFFIRMED.
